1. create solutions.py file 

2. create and install virtual env 
MAC: python3 -env venv venv
Windows: python -m <name_of_env>

3. Activate env
MAC: source venv/bin/activate
Windows: .\<name_of_env>\scripts\activate

*make sure to have admin rights on execution policy 
>>run powershell as admin
>> Set-ExecutionPolicy Unrestricted
>> Select yes

4. install API request library
MAC: pip3 install requests
Windows: pip install requests